<plot>Two hit men, Arch and Gamble, wander the halls of a boring office building looking for their target: a man named "Mark". They have no idea where he is or what he looks like. Meanwhile, a man named Mark Thompson, is spending what he thinks is just another boring day at work when really he is caught in a terrible cross fire of one huge misunderstanding.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?569804</url></doc>
